> Okay the Orc Fingerbones drop off of Orc Pawns in G-Fay. That's where I got both of mine. There is a bandit camp in G-Fay and I killed exactly two bandits and got the golden bandit tooth. So now it's down to the Orc Fibulas. I need 2 of them. One of the legplates, one for the tunic. From what I hear these drop off Orc Slavers in the cave in Crushbone. My ranger is level 10 and I've had no trouble acquiring any of these items. The Orc Slavers con yellow to me at 10. I can kill them with help.
